title: Spyder Auto Installation: LED Halo Headlights Install Overview
description: This video offers a general walkthrough of installing a set of headlights with LED-based Halo headlights. Several high-end luxury cars feature "halos" in their headlights and this video will show you how to wire your set to achieve the same look.
tags: Spyder Headlights, LED Halo lights, how to install, FAQ, LED headlight wiring guide
